'''索納絲·辛哈'''（[[印度語|印度語]]：सोनाक्षी सिन्हा，{{lang-en|Sonakshi Sinha}}，{{bd|1987年|6月2日|catIdx=Sinha, Sonakshi}}）是[[印度|印度]]女演員，父母均是演員。2010年，她和男影星[[薩爾曼·汗|薩爾曼·汗]]合作並在拍攝了她首套電影《寶萊塢之爆裂警官》 （Dabangg），該電影票房大賣也使她知名度提升<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Dabangg-17th-on-list-of-highest-grossers/articleshow/6633161.cms "'Dabangg' 17th on list of highest grossers "] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Dabangg-17th-on-list-of-highest-grossers/articleshow/6633161.cms |date=20160127185655 }} Business of Cinema, 27 September 2010.</ref>。辛哈也因此獲得第56屆[[印度電影觀眾獎|印度電影觀眾獎]]的最佳女新人獎項。<ref>[http://www.glamsham.com/movies/scoops/11/jan/31-56th-filmfare-awards-2010-a-night-of-glitz-n-glamour-011105.asp "56th Filmfare Awards 2010- A night of glitz & glamour"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.glamsham.com/movies/scoops/11/jan/31-56th-filmfare-awards-2010-a-night-of-glitz-n-glamour-011105.asp |date=20110203012043 }} Glamsham, 31 January 2011.</ref>

之後，她開始在不同電影中擔任女主角。2013年，辛哈和男演員[[蘭威爾·辛格|蘭威爾·辛格]]拍攝愛情電影《剪不斷的愛》（Lootera），此電影大獲好評<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Lootera-a-slow-pace-romantic-saga-worth-watching-say-critics/Article1-1087457.aspx "Lootera: a slow pace romantic saga worth watching, say critics"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Lootera-a-slow-pace-romantic-saga-worth-watching-say-critics/Article1-1087457.aspx |date=20131112201259 }} Hindustan Times, 5 July 2013.</ref>。而辛哈受讚賞的演出<ref>[http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/shatrughan-sinha-breaks-down-after-watching-daughter-sonakshi-in-lootera/1139060/ "Shatrughan Sinha breaks down after watching daughter Sonakshi in Lootera"] {{Wayback|url=http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/shatrughan-sinha-breaks-down-after-watching-daughter-sonakshi-in-lootera/1139060/ |date=20160127185655 }}, The Indian Express, 8 July 2013.</ref>為她帶來多項提名，其中包括[[印度電影觀眾獎|印度電影觀眾獎]]<ref>[http://www.filmfare.com/news/59th-idea-filmfare-awards-nominations-5138.html "59th Idea Filmfare Awards Nominations"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmfare.com/news/59th-idea-filmfare-awards-nominations-5138.html |date=20140115044052 }}, Filmfare, 13 January 2014.</ref>及[[國際印度電影大獎頒獎禮|國際印度電影大獎頒獎禮]]的最佳女主角提名<ref>[http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/6193 "Nominations for IIFA Awards 2014"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/6193 |date=20140221101141 }}, Bollywood Hungama, 20 February 2014.</ref>。

